 Problem Statement
Financial fraud is increasing rapidly with the growth of digital payments. Traditional systems struggle to detect fraud in real-time and lack transparency in handling suspicious transactions.

Key challenges include:

 Delayed fraud detection
 Lack of real-time monitoring
 Data tampering risks
 Limited transparency in transaction logs
 Difficulty in identifying complex fraud patterns


• Solution Overview

SecurePay AI is a full-stack web application that combines Artificial Intelligence and Blockchain to provide a secure and intelligent fraud detection system.

 How it works:
User inputs transaction data (amount, location, device, etc.)
AI model analyzes the transaction in real-time
System generates:
Fraud probability score
Risk level (Low / Medium / High)
If fraud is detected:
Alert is triggered
Transaction is stored on blockchain
Dashboard displays analytics and insights


