⚙️ Setup Instructions
1️⃣ Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/securepay-ai.git
cd securepay-ai
2️⃣ Backend Setup (Flask)
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
3️⃣ Frontend Setup (Angular)
cd frontend
npm install
ng serve
4️⃣ AI Model Setup
cd ml-model
python train_model.py
5️⃣ Blockchain Setup
cd blockchain
npm install
npx hardhat compile
npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network testnet
6️⃣ Firebase Configuration

Add your Firebase config in the frontend:

const firebaseConfig = {
  apiKey: "AIzaSyCuBxOgLIXHT54Q6oTO06fFohugieAYsiI",
  authDomain: "ai-blockchain-9c14e.firebaseapp.com",
  projectId: "ai-blockchain-9c14e",
  storageBucket: "ai-blockchain-9c14e.firebasestorage.app",
  messagingSenderId: "917986154808",
  appId: "1:917986154808:web:b2dfa851558e0c4fa889cd",
  measurementId: "G-Q7K04VP0EK"
};

 Run the Application
Frontend: http://localhost:4200
Backend API: http://localhost:5000
 Output
Real-time fraud detection
Risk-based alerts
Blockchain-secured transaction logs
Interactive analytics dashboard

